Changes:
• kind() now returns BrainKind instead of &'static str
• tick() uses fixed-size arrays (stack-allocated)
• mutate() accepts dyn RngCore instead of generic Rng
• runner() convenience function for quick registration

Naming convention:
• "ml.candle", "ml.tract-onnx", "ml.tch": Namespaced brain kinds
• Prevents collision with user-defined brains
• Future: Registry can filter by prefix (e.g., all "ml.*" brains)

